<br>
&quot;It was a well-done piece, very favorable. Russ Durkee (founder of MASA) got a great sound bite. The ATF was a no show. The post office promised to follow the law. An adult hobbiest (hobby store employee, I think) launched a rocket and talked intelligently about the safety of the hobby and the need not to overreact. <br>
